text: More people should check this out! Pardon my photo quality but this Korean burger was so good. It had this crispy yet juicy chicken patty coated in delicious sauce, paired with a slice of cheese and some cold red cabbage(?) that was really refreshing. The flavours and textures came together so well from start to end.

I went to this place with my friends. Everything was good. But the service was a bit slow i saw only one person who taking the food order serving the food and made a drinks for us drinks was very nice we asked to the guy what drink name he said its valentine special drink name cupid love we love it must visit to this place try drinks and food fish amristari bombay aloo was so goodüç∏
Super cosy cafe with nice Indian- Korean fusion food. The place has a few big TV screens that showed live premier league matches as well. Will sure return again to support!

We had a Dinner here on my B' day with my son. The ambience of Bar and Restaurant  good! Food also very tasty and had a different  style than other normal N Indian ones nearby Tanjong Katong area. The pepper Chicken Tandoor was excellent!

I cam here 3 times.

The food is really good. The bartender are friendly and easygoing.

The place quite chill, located in quiet neighbours, good for meeting friends and chat
